  "subject": "Remove legacy dependencies",
  "commit_message": "Remove legacy dependencies\n\n- Replace jsonschemafriend with com.networknt:json-schema-validator\n  which is already used in Policy Parent\n- Remove misplaced \"uniqueItems\" keyword from operational policy\n  schema (caused false validation failures with the new library)\n- Remove the following dependencies and replace with standard Java:\n  commons-io, commons-beanutils, guava, plexus-utils\n\nIssue-ID: POLICY-5592\nChange-Id: Ib5c5cd2921f8788f228990fde221bf3e6ebc16b0\nSigned-off-by: danielhanrahan <daniel.hanrahan@est.tech>\n",
